<paragraphs xml:id="the-plan-19">
<title>The Plan</title>

<p> By studying a few real-world mathematical models, we
will see a new dimension of mathematical work - more graphical and
artistic, but rooted in calculus nonetheless.<!-- linebreak -->
</p>


